  "notes": "Kazakh in Cyrillic script (Kazakhstan official orthography). 14-vowel system with front/back harmony. Қ = uvular /q/; Ғ = /ʁ/; Ң = /ŋ/; Ұ = back unrounded /ʊ/; Ү = /y/; І = /ɪ/. Transitioning to Latin script (phased 2017–2025, not yet complete).",
